Description:
Annotation on the envelope: ""Rubens Briefe, Fotokopien nach: Codex Diplomaticus Rubenianus Ruelens-Rooses" addressed (inside) to "Herrn Prof. Evers Technische Hochschule Kunsthistorisches Institut Darmstadt" and dated 08.05.1967

  • Translations of Rubens' letters to Pierre Dupuy and Peter van Veen (in german)
  • Transcription of Rubens' letters to Annibale Chieppio, Pierre van Veen, Valavez, Pierre Dupuy, Gevartius and Frederic de Marselaer (in italian and dutch)
